## Bipa/r\_t.ligaisan Infrastructure Law

In November 2021, President Biden signed a $1 trillion Bipa/r\_t.ligaisan Infrastructure Law, unlocking funds for new spending on roads, bridges, aqueducts, broadband and other projects in /fi.ligascal years 2022-2026.

