- · freezing Russian assets in the euro area;
- · imposing expo/r\_t.liga control measures (including a ban on the expo/r\_t.liga of goods to Russia and Belarus in the aviation, maritime, space, technology and 'dual-use' sectors);
- · excluding major Russian banks from the international SWIFT transaction system;
