- · blocking current accounts with the Sberbank banking group;
- · freezing the personal assets of the Russian President, oligarchs, politicians and senior executives of the Russian companies that suppo/r\_t.liga him.
- · closing airspace to Russian /fl.ligaights;

These sanctions have had an initial impact on the exchange rate of the ruble, which has depreciated sharply against the euro and the US dollar, on local interest rates (which  were  increased  to  20%  by  the  Russian  Central Bank) and on the share prices of companies listed on the Moscow Stock Exchange (with a signi/fi.ligacant decline being recorded in March).

